data.description: Charming Cape Cod is waiting for you!  On the exterior, you will find a nice backyard with a lovely brick patio as well as an area which currently has a stand alone firepit. Inside you will find a living room which is a nice place to unwind at the end of the day. Lovely eat in kitchen to show off your cooking skills.  Two bedrooms on the first floor as well as a third bedroom on the second floor.  Call today for a showing.
